AB  - Context: Ethnic groups differ in fragility fracture risk and bone metabolism. Differences in diurnal rhythms (DRs) of bone turnover and PTH may play a role.
   Objective: Weinvestigated the DRs of plasma bone turnover markers (BTMs), PTH, and 1,25(OH)(2)D in three groups with pronounced differences in bone metabolism and plasma PTH.
